OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FA lack of progress on the Hillsborough
OL,7,FLaw to prevent future cover-ups is "an
OL,8,Finsult" to victims of major disasters
OL,9,Fand their families, campaigners have
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FCampaigners have described a lack of
OL,13,Fprogress on the Hillsborough Law to
OL,14,Fprevent future cover-ups "an insult"
OL,15,Fto victims of major disasters and
OL,16,Ftheir families.
OL,26,@oD@dOUpD@GO]vD@ZOUvD@dO]
