PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FPeople affected by the Hillsborough
OL,7,Ftragedy, and Manchester Arena terror
OL,8,Fattack, alongside victims of the
OL,9,Finfected blood and Horizon Post Office
OL,10,Fscandals, have written to the prime
OL,11,Fminister to express their frustration.
OL,13,FThe Labour Government proposed a duty
OL,14,Fof candour as part of the Public
OL,15,FOffice (Accountability) Bill - also
OL,16,Fknown as the Hillsborough Law - to
OL,17,Fmeet a manifesto pledge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FThe campaigners say the bill's delay
OL,7,Fhas undermined their trust in the
OL,8,FGovernment, and has had a "serious,
OL,9,Fnegative impact on countless families."
OL,11,FThe proposed legislation takes its
OL,12,Fname from the Hillsborough disaster,
OL,13,Fafter which families campaigned for
OL,14,Fyears to get to the truth behind what
OL,15,Fcaused the crush which led to the
OL,16,Fdeath of 97 football fans at the FA
OL,17,FCup semi-final between Liverpool and
OL,18,FNottingham Forest in 1989.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FIt would create a duty for public
OL,7,Fauthorities and public officials to
OL,8,Falways act "with candour, transparency
OL,9,Fand frankness in their dealings with
OL,10,Finquiries and investigations", and to
OL,11,Fflag information to inquiry and
OL,12,Finvestigation leaders, if they think
OL,13,Fit is relevant.
OL,15,FBut its progress through Parliament
OL,16,Fhas stalled amid a row over whether
OL,17,Fpeople in organisations such as MI5
OL,18,Fand MI6 would be subject to the same
OL,19,Fduties as other public servants.
OL,26,@pD@LOUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FA coalition of campaigners, which
OL,7,Fdescribes itself as being "made up of
OL,8,Fvictims of some of the worst
OL,9,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,10,Fhistory" and those "affected by
OL,11,Findividual state-related deaths", said
OL,12,Fthe process to get to this stage has
OL,13,F"taken too long".
OL,26,@oD@[OUrD@HO]rD@TOUsD@`O]uD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FIn their letter to Sir Keir Starmer on
OL,7,F23 March, they said: "In total, we
OL,8,Frepresent thousands of ordinary people
OL,9,Fwho have made fighting to ensure that
OL,10,Ffamilies in the future do not
OL,11,Fexperience the lies and cover-ups
OL,12,Fwhich we all have as our collective
OL,13,Fgoal."
OL,15,FThere had already been a delay in the
OL,16,FBill being introduced to Parliament,
OL,17,Fbecause of drafting issues, and a
OL,18,Fpromise to bring in the law by the
OL,19,F36th anniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,20,Fdisaster, on April 15 2025, was missed.
OL,26,@oD@VOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FIt was eventually introduced in
OL,7,FSeptember 2025, but has been delayed
OL,8,Fsince an amendment was pulled at the
OL,9,Feleventh hour in January over concerns
OL,10,Fit could provide a get-out clause for
OL,11,Fspies.
OL,13,FConcerns were raised that intelligence
OL,14,Fagencies could have used the amendment
OL,15,Fto avoid being bound by the proposed
OL,16,Fduty of candour.
OL,18,FIn their letter to the PM, campaigners
OL,19,Fsaid: "Another anniversary of the
OL,20,FHillsborough disaster is fast
OL,21,Fapproaching. Yet the Bill has stalled.
OL,26,@{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,F"We understand it will have to roll
OL,7,Fover to the next parliamentary session
OL,8,Fbut have been given no clarity as to
OL,9,Fwhat the Government intends to do,
OL,10,Fbeyond meaningless reassurances that
OL,11,Fit is being worked on.
OL,13,F"Ultimately, there is no end in sight."
OL,15,FThey say the delay is "having a
OL,16,Fserious, negative impact on countless
OL,17,Fother families affected by or yet to
OL,18,Fbe affected by state-related deaths
OL,19,Fand on the wider public".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUuD@gO]wD@WOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,FThe campaigners have urged the PM to
OL,7,Fmeet them "before Easter to avoid
OL,8,Ffurther delay" and to "commit to a
OL,9,Fdate when the Bill will return to the
OL,10,FCommons for Report Stage".
OL,12,FThey added: "The fact that
OL,13,FHillsborough Law has still not been
OL,14,Freintroduced to Parliament is an
OL,15,Finsult to all of us who have been
OL,16,Fworking so hard to get to this point.
OL,18,F"It has undermined our trust in this
OL,19,FGovernment to do what they said they
OL,20,Fwould and make this legacy project a
OL,21,Freality.
OL,26,@oD@KOUpD@NO]pD@WOUrD@YO]tD@MOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774357890
OL,3,CSlow progress of Hillsborough Law Bill
OL,4,C'an insult'
OL,6,F"We hope that, going forward, you the
OL,7,FPrime Minister and your Government
OL,8,Fwill listen to the people Hillsborough
OL,9,FLaw is meant to protect and not those
OL,10,Fit is meant to protect us from. We
OL,11,Fhave suffered enough."
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@VO]
